{"tid":603810,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"討論吓send email既manner","createTime":"2018-03-24T05:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T05:49:48.000Z","uid":171594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb18c6aa118dd368ee8f9d1f69be8596f2d50586","tid":603810,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"有時啲工作需要俾幾個同事知<br />\n就會to某個人，再cc其他人<br />\n但偏偏有啲閪人剩係reply你一個<br />\n有時我行開行埋，miss咗冇睇就仆街<br />\n又要我再fwd你封野俾相關同事<br />\nSend黎send去搞到亂Q晒<br />\n正正經經撳個reply all再覆係咪咁難？<br />\n<br />\n同一單job本來好好地reply同一封email溝通<br />\n有啲閪人無神神send個新email過黎<br />\n搞到亂晒不突止，想搵啲之前既對話又麻煩<br />\n<br />\n某程度上，呢種人係拖慢緊成個工作效率<br />\n理應拉去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6f11f49c78a1e96d2654128d730b9c81fdffa6","tid":603810,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"有d野唔一定要reply all，就係唔想比人睇"},{"pid":"94cde7d7f0bc5550a9cd094cbadd8c9fcfd7acd8","tid":603810,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca6f11f49c78a1e96d2654128d730b9c81fdffa6","tid":603810,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"有d野唔一定要reply all，就係唔想比人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"就係講緊個樣野需要俾其他人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}